We project a slight decrease in General Fund revenue from the

06:09.248 --> 06:12.586
FY 22 projection due to a reduction in the

06:12.608 --> 06:16.102
number of backlog cases and a continued lower citation

06:16.166 --> 06:20.074
rates. Next slide, please. This slide

06:20.122 --> 06:23.402
includes revenue highlights for our four MCD

06:23.466 --> 06:26.718
special funds. The annual variances in

06:26.724 --> 06:30.318
the revenue budgets for the funds remain in line with the General

06:30.404 --> 06:33.746
Fund for FY 23. We anticipate a

