Through this grant, we have been able to expand our program to additional

06:44.850 --> 06:49.174
schools. However, this reduction may negatively impact the

06:49.212 --> 06:53.154
services we provide to our partner school districts. Next slide,

06:53.202 --> 06:56.906
please. This slide represents a

06:56.928 --> 06:59.962
comparison of expenditures for FY 21,

07:00.096 --> 07:03.434
FY 22 and FY 23 for all

07:03.472 --> 07:07.542
MCD funds and the percentage change between FY

07:07.606 --> 07:10.930
23 proposed and FY 22 budgets.

07:11.030 --> 07:15.230
There is a 2.3 overall increase in expenditures across

07:15.300 --> 07:18.302
all MCD funds for FY 23.

07:18.436 --> 07:19.760
Next slide, please.

