80% of the General Fund expenditure budget consists of

07:25.352 --> 07:29.326
personnel cost. The remaining 20% is non

07:29.358 --> 07:32.858
personnel costs that include inner fund accounts, CSMART,

07:32.894 --> 07:36.274
support supplies and services. Next slide,

07:36.322 --> 07:36.920
please.

07:38.570 --> 07:42.354
99% of the building security fund expenditure

07:42.402 --> 07:45.782
budget is non personnel and it includes contract

07:45.846 --> 07:49.334
security services. The remaining 1% of the budget

