is personnel and is related to the retiree health benefits

07:53.152 --> 07:55.340
cost. Next slide, please.

07:56.750 --> 08:00.490
The majority of the court technology fund expenditure budget

08:00.570 --> 08:03.790
is nonpersonal. It includes software and

08:03.940 --> 08:06.490
hardware licensing, maintenance costs,

08:06.570 --> 08:10.374
CSMART support and other planned technology enhancements.

08:10.522 --> 08:13.906
The remaining 18% is personnel cost.

08:14.008 --> 08:17.666
Next slide, please. 90% of

08:17.688 --> 08:21.778
the local Tourancy Prevention and Diversion Fund

