expenditure budget is personnel costs. The remaining

08:25.682 --> 08:29.046
10% is non personnel cost, including education

08:29.148 --> 08:32.566
and training supplies, as well as teen court and

08:32.588 --> 08:35.610
student engagement activities. Next slide.

08:36.990 --> 08:40.682
This worksheet provides an overview of the expenditure net

08:40.736 --> 08:44.182
change between the FY 22 and the FY

08:44.246 --> 08:47.854
23 General Fund budgets. FY 23

08:47.892 --> 08:51.402
reflects a 2.2% increase in expenditures.

08:51.546 --> 08:55.162
This increase is due to the resumption of dockets and the related

08:55.226 --> 08:59.118
increases in court services, noticing jury cost,

08:59.204 --> 09:02.778
postage language services, variances in the inner

09:02.794 --> 09:06.770
fund accounts, pension and health benefit rates, and the two Hope

09:06.840 --> 09:09.940
3% increases. Next slide, please.

