This slide provides our FY 23 expenditure highlights

09:14.770 --> 09:17.906
for the General Fund. We will continue to maintain

09:17.938 --> 09:21.522
the court CSMART System fund, contractual increases

09:21.586 --> 09:25.302
in the security and armored car service, language services,

09:25.436 --> 09:28.870
passport program costs, and citation book printing.

09:28.950 --> 09:32.694
Next slide, please. This slide provides

09:32.742 --> 09:36.614
expenditure highlights for our four special revenue funds.

09:36.742 --> 09:40.686
Expenditures in these funds include contract security services,

09:40.868 --> 09:44.794
technology maintenance and enhancement cost, and Truancy

09:44.842 --> 09:48.394
prevention services. Two of these four funds include

09:48.442 --> 09:50.770
personnel cost. Next slide.

